
# Message should conform to the following:
#   :emoji: (#ticket) [topic] Verb-leading short description

# Where emoji is based on Havoc Spec and is one of:
#   features: tada books sparkles construction zap wheelchair abc lock
#   fixmes:   bug wastebasket
#   other:    rat flags guard ledger package recycle poop wrench bricks key alien robot alembic stethoscope thread
#   breaking: boom
#   crises:   ambulance rewind

# Example:
#   :sparkles: (#123) [i18n] Add proper diacritics to frobnicator

